05Dt 31:14 Then the LORD said to Moses, "The time has come for you to die. Call Joshua and present yourselves at the Tabernacle¨ç, so that I may commission him there." So Moses and Joshua went and presented themselves at the Tabernacle. / ¨ç{Hebrew Tent of Meeting; also in 31.14b}
