05Dt 31:23 Then the LORD commissioned Joshua son of Nun with these words£º "Be strong and courageous, for you must bring the people of Israel into the land I swore to give them. I will be with you."
05Dt 31:24 When Moses had finished writing this entire body of instruction in a book,
