091Sm 28:20 Saul fell full length on the ground, paralyzed with fright because of Samuel's words. He was also faint with hunger, for he had eaten nothing all day and all night.
091Sm 28:21 When the woman saw how distraught he was, she said, "Sir, I obeyed your command at the risk of my life.
